name: Coastal Crave

reviews.review_text:
After reading the reviews for this place we had to give it a try & it did not disappoint !

Shantosh was a fantastic host, the food was beautiful and cooked to perfection with great presentation and the drinks were just as good!

It was that good we have booked up for our final evening and our friend’s bday party before we leave GOA.

Thank you to Shantosh & the team - wonderful chilled evening!

Craig & Sara

Been there 3 times in 5 days .
decent quality and big portions.
Got quote for 3k for tandoori fish at curry house then we got same tandoori fish here for only 1200
Plus they have open kitchen looks very clean
Superb ambience with music, perfect location and great food. Good place for a slow and lazy meal. Cocktails are wonderful.

description:
**Restaurant Review: Coastal Crave**

Tucked away in the vibrant locale of Candolim, Coastal Crave has garnered an impressive rating of 4.9 from a remarkable 536 reviewers, solidifying its status as a must-visit destination for food lovers. This coastal gem is particularly celebrated for its cocktails and the excellent musical atmosphere it provides, making it an ideal spot for an evening out. As reflected in customer feedback, the restaurant also serves delicious, sizeable portions of seafood and other culinary delights.

**Ambiance & Design**

Coastal Crave greets its guests with a superb ambiance that sets the stage for a memorable dining experience. The décor features a pleasing blend of coastal elements and contemporary design, subtly enriched by warm lighting that adds to the inviting atmosphere. Guests have noted the charm of the open kitchen, allowing diners to catch a glimpse of the culinary team at work, which not only enhances transparency but also instills confidence in the cleanliness and quality of the kitchen. Accompanied by soothing music, the restaurant serves as a perfect backdrop for both leisurely meals and celebratory gatherings, as highlighted by various reviews.

![Restaurant Ambiance](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdl8PScY6YRycqcnFskwNcxcdxApAWOcA8VQNI0fza3qbEB5SLNOLnyShlz-wxWrEESNn8MMgKq8UFwpBKsJ3HKghA-eq-Y8_Fn8lqdCavaMr8rs0ahDCRAjKe_-fNdYPmFaGDe2=w375-h281-p)

**Menu & Culinary Experience**

The menu at Coastal Crave offers a delectable variety, with many customers praising their signature dishes, particularly the tandoori fish. One patron highlighted a significant cost-saving when opting for the restaurant's version compared to prices quoted elsewhere. This assurance of both quality and value leads to repeat visits—some guests returning multiple times in just a few days. The presentations of the dishes have received accolades for their aesthetic appeal, enhancing the dining experience. Moreover, the cocktails are highly regarded, touted as wonderful complements to the meal, and a cornerstone of the overall experience.

![Food Presentation](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdkC95sdSqBavYZkefc9-wibrEkfC_0KCHNiYnw8cjhuRrAPacGEa1a9fjmsnegL2PP0uZK030jrklHqWaUlDU3DJU4vPQ-6mf7_wmWq9RdEWlq3AVucRsaEijd5raMjOOjBKIPO_Q=w750-h563-p)

**Customer Experience & Service**

Feedback regarding the service consistently emphasizes the friendly demeanor of the staff, notably singling out Shantosh for his exceptional hospitality. The team at Coastal Crave seems to share a collective commitment to ensuring diners have a relaxed and enjoyable experience, as noted in several reviews. The restaurant has also organized arrangements for special evenings, underscoring its adaptability to customers' needs whether walk-ins or reservations.

**Popularity & Reviews**

With an ever-growing base of positive reviews and high social media engagement, Coastal Crave has swiftly become a local favorite. The combination of excellent food, a vibrant atmosphere with live music, and reasonable pricing has put Coastal Crave on the culinary map of Goa. This reception reflects not just luck but a concerted effort to provide a dining experience that resonates with visitors and locals alike.

![Guest Experience](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdnZXtRsOMppPhofhy9xDKBEL_-DUh6g8KMXtLLh9P_44fYA_gm4aBlTQiuNdr61GupBkqYvge05xjq_gtiONKjKHGfnoPZ6poC0yFCi6_WEf2ilrDbYzIwA1oGTMChZ7Hb2di8=w375-h281-p)

**Final Thoughts**

In summary, Coastal Crave stands out not only for its remarkable cuisine and cocktails but also for its inviting atmosphere and attentive service. It has successfully created a space where diners can enjoy exceptional food while soaking in the enchanting coastal vibes of Candolim. Whether you're celebrating a special occasion or simply seeking a delightful meal, Coastal Crave promises an experience that is hard to forget. This will undoubtedly remain a highlight of anyone's culinary journey in Goa.
